name: Hindsight
Lore: '''I''m backwards! You fleabitten furball...only an overgrown mophead like you would be stupid enough--''',
Text: 'Deploy on C-3PO. Eyes In The Dark, The Professor, Mantellian Savrip and Hopping Mad are immune to Alter. Also, at the end of every turn, unless C-3PO is present with a Wookiee, you may examine the cards in your Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
